message.entry: CHECKBOXLABELS, DEFAULTVARIABLENAMES and ITEMSTOEXPORT must all be cell arrays
Default variable names must be a string array or cell array of character vectors.
Default variable names must be unique
SELECTED must be a logical array
CHECKBOXLABELS, DEFAULTVARIABLENAMES and ITEMSTOEXPORT must all be the same length
SELECTED must be the same length as ITEMSTOEXPORT
FUNCTIONLIST must be the same length as ITEMSTOEXPORT
